T1  - CREDIBILITY AND STRATEGIC LEARNING IN NETWORKS
AU  - Chatterjee, Kalyan
AU  - Dutta, Bhaskar
Y1  - 2016/08/01
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2016/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12175
